{"tid":1633464,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[和您大辨論]邊個話和理無野可以做？全民廣場論政","createTime":"2019-10-07T04:08:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T04:46:08.000Z","uid":71345,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d80440f0b92972187976217a2c4cb058460027b4","tid":1633464,"uid":71345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:08:12.000Z","msg":"好多屋苑都有羅馬廣場，係時候組織返幾十場大辨論，目標係廣傳理念，全民論政，辨明是非。<br />\n<br />\n目標對象：廢老<br />\n目標：讓廢年成為老兵，加入和理/勇武陣營<br />\n<br />\n物資：<br />\n大聲公x1<br />\n和理演說員x1-2<br />\n拍攝x1<br />\n<br />\n方法：<br />\n於廣場發表言論，尋求街坊為香港社會發聲，不論立場，然後邀請任何人發言。<br />\n<br />\n重點：<br />\n以溫和的語氣暴露廢老們的邏輯謬誤，巧妙地引導廢老們意識到一切亂局皆因政府，並宣讓人民有推翻暴政的責任。<br />\n<br />\n忌：<br />\n動手<br />\n<br />\n建議日子：<br />\n平日夜晚"},{"pid":"c74b1762271294d63ad97ffa21ac4fbd39d551bb","tid":1633464,"uid":128735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:09:04.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91ee3d04f4b55c7f50893b305065b744cfac1cc4","tid":1633464,"uid":71345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:17:19.000Z","msg":"求推<br />\n1/10"},{"pid":"57b9765d9c77a9a41b5e63ca3ecea46d2f4d5b17","tid":1633464,"uid":71345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:23:34.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n2"},{"pid":"24600516b8dffc6b2484b49c01ed44db7e0c1f71","tid":1633464,"uid":71345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:46:08.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n3"}]}